[If insecticide spraying is, at this point, intended only to reduce
mosquito populations in general and not to reduce populations of vector
species, i.e., _Aedes aegypti_, this is a p.r. effort, not a control
effort. Eradication "within a month" (or a year) is unlikely. - Mod.CHC
